Duvidas ou sugestões: igreja@tabernaculodafe.org.br

FeWo2Go is the first app to Kempten's annual Allgäuer Festwoche – also known as FeWo. 
The famous Allgäuer Festwoche is the largest trade fair in the region of Allgäu (Bavaria, Germany) and belongs to the largest consumer trade fairs in Germany. Through the broad range of cultural attraction and the several parties in connection with the event FeWo has become the most important social event in the Allgäu. With FeWo2Go you have the whole spectrum of information in your pocket, whether you are a daily or evening visitor. From general information, such as opening times, prices, to detailed information on exhibitors, public transport and the after show parties – FeWo2Go offers everything which your heart desires.

The map, which is also available offline, provides an overall view of the entire area with all relevant locations. The related information button goes one step further and gives you all relevant information about the specific location. Additionally, the FeWo2Go App assists you in not only finding your own position, but rather allows you to send it to your friends to arrange a meeting point. If you are still lost FeWo2Go helps you to direct you by calculating the route. 

In the Company tab FeWo2Go lists all exhibitors, including exhibition hall and stand. Depending on the type of company, you have the possibility to access a business profile and the option to contact them directly.

Work hard, play hard! The "fifth season" combines both of each. Throughout the day visitors have the chance to buy various items, in the evening however FeWo is popular for old and young alike.
